title: MMBN5: Team Colonel Any% No ASE

text.text:
ACDC 1: 
Grab GMDs
Grab BMD (800 Zenny)
Jack in to PC, do tutorials

ACDC 2: 
Grab GMDs
Buy HP Memory from shop
Yai’s room: Talk to her, turn on furnace, jack into her HP and get BMD (RegUp2)
Dex’s room: Talk to him, jack into his HP grab BMDs (RegUp1 and HP Memory)
Jack into tree: Grab BMD (HP memory)
Jack into right chip statue: Grab BMD (HP Memory)
Talk to trash can for RegUp1
Go into lab and end up in ACDC areas
Activate SneakRun and go all the way to end of ACDC 2 and win battle
Run into locked door in the lab
Dad’s lab, get his ID from desk, jack into his comp and grab BMD (RegUp2)
R -> O -> T -> A -> L -> BLANK   OWL RAT
H -> C -> L -> D -> A -> BLANK   DOCK HALL
H -> E -> M -> T -> I -> A -> BLANK   HIP TOE ARM

Folder Edit:
Sort reverse MB,
First WideSword <-> First Sword,
Slot 1 <-> Cannon A,
Reg AreaGrab,
Remove recovs,
Add good things
Talk to Baryl then go to sleep
Grab GMDs and buy SneakRun x1
Colonel: ScrenDiv in front of the Guardian
MegaMan: Block in front of BlizzardMan
Jack into Mayl’s PC, get MaylBanr
Go to FurnaceComp, grab BMD  (HP Memory) go straight up
Talk to Mr. Prog at the very end
Meet friends in front of the station

Folder edit:
Sort MB
Remove CrackOut and Guard1
Add DarkSword, BlizzMan, BusterUp,
Sort reverse MB,
AirShot near the top,

Oran Area 1:
Grab GMDs
Run to the end of the screen
Get bamboo, fishing line, and worm, then talk to Dex and go fishing
Get board, DryGrass, and twig, then talk to Dex
Enter Mine and go straight up to blue elevator
Go up the ramp and jack into the thing, get MineKey
Go back through the door, get HP Memory from crates
Go to DrillComps and fight doors
Grab all GMDs in DrillComps, and fight Drills for up to 4 DrillArms
Nothing to grab, just GMDs and DrillArms

Folder Edit:
Reg AirShot,
Remove Vulcans and Minibombs,
Add Drills, LongSword, RockCube, Invis
SneakRun and over to Oran Area 3
Buy HP Memory if enough money
MegaMan: LongSword to open way to Guardian
MegaMan: LongSword to get Zenny on the far right
Colonel: ScrenDiv to open way to ShadowMan
Colonel: ScrenDiv in front of ShadowMan

1: Right
9: Forward
10: BMD then Left
11: BMD then Right
14: Forward
16: Talk to ShadowMan
Use SneakRun after every expiration (2 total)

Folder Edit:
Remove Cannons,
Add AntiFire, FastGauge, Django, ShadeMan
Jack into PC SneakRun  and buy 4x SneakRuns then early PastKey

Drill Comps:
SneakRun (4 total), run to end, get GMDs if needed
Talk to Baryl in Mission Control
Buy 4x SneakRuns and head all the way to Oran Areas
Use SneakRun (2 total) for Cloud Scenario
Straight path clearing clouds to Oran 2
Talk to Prog to empty the vacuum
Dark cloud on the left, then clear with the Prog
White -> Gray -> White -> White -> White to Prog
Gray to Prog, then towards SciLab2
Straight until Prog, clear with him
Gray, down to white, yellow, clear with Prog
Up to thunder, right to yellow and clear with Prog
Left to 2 black clouds, clear with prog
Up to thunder, back down to Prog
Back up to white, gray, gray, gray
Over to the dark clouds in SciLab3
